1.0.1.name: wordpress/omnigallery
1.0.1.description: Enhance your WordPress website with the OmniGallery Photo Gallery. You can easily add your photo from Instagram, Pinterest, Picasa, Flickr, Facebook, and Dribble into your Wordpress Gallery. Adding the gallery is very simple, you just have to add new post/page, then select gallery icon, select omnigallery then you can select which gallery you want to fetch your images to your blog. You can add multiple gallery on the same post/page.
